{"word":"νείαιρα","slug":"νείαιρα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>νείαιρα</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:irregular'>irreg.</a> <a href='S:feminine'>fem.</a> <a href='S:Comparative'>comp.</a> (<a href='S:confer, compare'>cf.</a> <a href='S:πρέσβειρα'><el>πρέσβειρα</el></a>) of <a href='S:νέος'><el>νέος</el></a>, as <el>νέατος, νείατος</el> is <a href='S:Superlative'>Sup.</a>\n<p/><i>lower</i>, <el>νειαίρῃ δ' ἐν γαστρί</el> in <i>the lower part of</i> the belly, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/>"}]}